<Rewrite PAsource="" >for </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >bright pupils </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >in </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >private schools</Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >. </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Mr Justice Maurice Kay </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >expressed deep unease at the Government's handling of the issue after hearing </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >a case </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >brought by a </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >mother </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >whose </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >daughter </Verbatim>
