<Verbatim PAsource="" >11 </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >has seen her hopes of a </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >place </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >dashed.</Rewrite>


<Rewrite PAsource="" >In </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >a test case </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >for around </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >1,500 </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >families, </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Rachel Begbie </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >argued that she and her </Rewrite>
